        "TileImage": "$($repository 965fdd6f-6aab-4743-9416-9831306bea48).Image",
        "Description": "Want to take down a corporation 47? Well todays your lucky day. Our client, wants us to take down Ether, a giant megacorporation in charge of many biological technology. To take down Ether however, we&apos;ll need to start slow. Our analysts have found that some of Ether&apos;s most trusted researchers, Kirsten Petersen and  Sister Lei, have been sent secretely to help out an illegal testing facility. Take them both down and we&apos;ll find the location of many other of Ether&apos;s projects. Good luck 47.",
